                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For the texts of telegrams 1196 and 1197, April 5, from Moscow, conveying the
                    text of the Soviet reply to the tripartite note of March 29, and the report of
                    Ambassador <persName corresp="#p_BCE1">Bohlen</persName>’s talk with <persName
                        corresp="#p_KVV1">Kuznetsov</persName> on April 5, see <ref target="#pg_70"
                        >pages 70</ref> and <ref target="#pg_71">71</ref>, respectively.</p>
            </div>
